{"tid":1661548,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[90's港星潮] 驚鴻一瞥的Chyna","createTime":"2019-10-18T07:17:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T06:42:08.000Z","uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e227c08287e41146631957d3f59b54dac89ba5b4","tid":1661548,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T07:17:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/n2ZRFpIwXvM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fn2ZRFpIwXvM&d=JQdTOMZ4NvWA5L1F4kLizzkC3bY0i4P88JjHF8GLL0M%3D&h=df618611\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/n2ZRFpIwXvM</a><br />\n<br />\n要說Chyna，就不能不提 Don Ashley 唐龍，他是一手組成這個樂團的人，在 Chyna 存在時仍是他的樂團。"},{"pid":"6c3fc6050eca8f4de6756e586058aba8c6548452","tid":1661548,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T07:17:27.000Z","msg":"唐龍 <strong>Donald James Ashley</strong>（1954年8月13日－2014年10月19），有「亞洲鼓王」的美譽，在組成Chyna之前，他是Ram Band的一員，Ram Band雖是香港樂隊，但成員之中只有他與吉他手Peter Ng屬華人，後來Ram Band的主音Jun逝世，Band也就解散。之後唐龍替夏韶聲的樂隊「Visa Band」鼓手替工，認識了當時Visa Band的成員黃良昇、蘇德華與單立文，四人在1983年組成新Band，由唐龍取名為「Chyna」。"},{"pid":"087a61cd1792aa8346edb8762f77819a3f6ce079","tid":1661548,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T07:17:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/w7uzs7WOlz4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fw7uzs7WOlz4&d=JQdTOMZ4NvWA5L1F4kLizzkC3bY0i4P88JjHF8GLL0M%3D&h=e99b4548\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/w7uzs7WOlz4</a>"},{"pid":"d9c1933e0c29a47db7bbb89f2d67f7bcbc1d0aa0","tid":1661548,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T07:18:19.000Z","msg":"第一張唱片《There is Rock &amp; Roll In China》，推出後打入美國Billboard，名曲〈Within You&rsquo;ll Remain〉。<br />\n<br />\nChyna 打出名堂後，唐龍與另外三位成員出現分歧而分道揚鑣，離開的三人後來組成「Blue Jeans」。"},{"pid":"6af7646d38f02da1fca3682c161c4ff6c5b2d0cb","tid":1661548,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T07:18:47.000Z","msg":"而唐龍找回了Peter Ng合作，隨後推出Chyna的第二張唱片《Back Together》，繼續打入Billboard排行榜；1988年Chyna出版了他們最滿意的唱片《灰色都市》，唱片裡有超過十分鐘的Drum Solo，中文歌詞更找來了林夕，可惜因政治題材遭電台禁播。在現在提起八十年代中後期的本地Band熱潮中，Chyna反而較少被提起。"},{"pid":"0d276d0d532f740085759f9c216eaf9f804b97f2","tid":1661548,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T07:24:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/WjA3Ko6FXxg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FWjA3Ko6FXxg&d=JQdTOMZ4NvWA5L1F4kLizzkC3bY0i4P88JjHF8GLL0M%3D&h=a17a3ae6\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/WjA3Ko6FXxg</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/l25rBZ1tkyg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fl25rBZ1tkyg&d=JQdTOMZ4NvWA5L1F4kLizzkC3bY0i4P88JjHF8GLL0M%3D&h=227fa085\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/l25rBZ1tkyg</a><br />\n<br />\n唐龍也與許多本地主流歌手合作過，包括徐小鳳、譚詠麟、張學友及關淑怡等，可能因為葉廣權監製的穿針引線。"},{"pid":"eb6cf4739e70b9ac246b033f3f1003481f56152a","tid":1661548,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T07:25:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/LXQ0c0RXacM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FLXQ0c0RXacM&d=JQdTOMZ4NvWA5L1F4kLizzkC3bY0i4P88JjHF8GLL0M%3D&h=61896214\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/LXQ0c0RXacM</a><br />\n<br />\n《灰色都市》之後幾年Chyna也沒有推出新作，直到1992年進軍台灣歌壇的重組。"},{"pid":"fee75cca09882a0386891f9f9cd034aabb6ad5ff","tid":1661548,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T07:27:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0AVKxRMYLtA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0AVKxRMYLtA&d=JQdTOMZ4NvWA5L1F4kLizzkC3bY0i4P88JjHF8GLL0M%3D&h=5cd3a9c0\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0AVKxRMYLtA</a><br />\n<br />\nChyna的首張國語唱片《答案》在1992年3月推出，這次重組成員除了唐龍與新的女主唱崔元姝外，還有本地知名製作人Richard Yuen等。"},{"pid":"dfcb05c4394e3447034309039a838bef750f556b","tid":1661548,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T07:28:26.000Z","msg":"1992年當時，台灣主流樂壇的樂隊風氣並不興盛，但唱片公司下了重本，該年五月為Chyna一連舉辦了十場中型演唱會演出，唱片的銷量不俗，據報載賣了四白金。"},{"pid":"3616bd737d84eec6b938662032f2173d005c69f3","tid":1661548,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T07:28:49.000Z","msg":"過了兩年，Chyna在台灣的第二張唱片卻又難產，官方說法是「團員召集不易，彼此對音樂理念又有不同的想法」，實際上就是唐龍跟Richard Yuen鬧翻，Richard Yuen要求成為Chyna團長，又開始頻繁的接外務，這正是唐龍所不喜（當年唐龍與Blue Jeans三人的分歧，據說也是三人的外務太多），而唐龍也因此被告上法庭，被禁止以Chyna之名工作三年，「Chyna」這個樂隊名字也從此在台灣銷聲匿跡，後來在台灣只有女主音崔元姝發行過個人唱片。"},{"pid":"bd3e005e3aa27be76a84f93ef0a1a7a2eb7b9416","tid":1661548,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T12:26:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/SY1eDI9gOXw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FSY1eDI9gOXw&d=JQdTOMZ4NvWA5L1F4kLizzkC3bY0i4P88JjHF8GLL0M%3D&h=b061a0a5\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/SY1eDI9gOXw</a><br />\n<br />\ng嬸推薦，在遠方 Chy！na！girl！😁"},{"pid":"ab12f71b25a97d461f0234ffa797fd6e9098d5a0","tid":1661548,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T12:27:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/q6r7vLQRxQA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fq6r7vLQRxQA&d=JQdTOMZ4NvWA5L1F4kLizzkC3bY0i4P88JjHF8GLL0M%3D&h=ebee0613\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/q6r7vLQRxQA</a><br />\n<br />\n黑！太！陽！😀"},{"pid":"66893160a37478636fd02ce59700845740a4b75d","tid":1661548,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T12:43:24.000Z","msg":"我好認同上面，真係八十尾九十d人只會記得太極 Radias Beyond 達明嗰d，藍戰士都話有人間中會提，反而我從來冇聽過人講 Chyna<br />\n<br />\n佢地其實係唯一隊較早期又上到外國Billboard既樂隊，應該多人識過其他 🙄"},{"pid":"3b2b25bae07b18eeb73978be130c25d6bcec4fb5","tid":1661548,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T15:09:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Ly-ieVbJAT8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FLy-ieVbJAT8&d=JQdTOMZ4NvWA5L1F4kLizzkC3bY0i4P88JjHF8GLL0M%3D&h=1030c4c8\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Ly-ieVbJAT